#
# Hospital ransomware crisis. 47 patients on life support. Exploit ENTROPY's
# backdoor to recover decryption keys before critical systems fail.
#
# ENTROPY Cell: Ransomware Incorporated
# Mission Type: Crisis Response / Recovery
# Difficulty: Beginner (Mission 2)
#
# NEW MECHANICS:
# - Guard patrol timing (60-second predictable loop)
# - PIN safe cracking (4-digit puzzle)
# - Moral dilemma interface (ransom decision)
#
# ROOM LAYOUT:
#   Reception → IT Department (locked-easy) → Server Room (locked-medium-hard)
